Architecture: armhf
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusMP - Termux 32-bit IMAP4rev1 Mail Server
 A high-performance IMAP4rev1 mail server for 32-bit ARM Termux.
 Supports IDLE, compression, STARTTLS, and advanced mail management.

