Package: nexus-rmc-termux32
Architecture: armhf
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusRMC - Termux 32-bit Remote Mail Client
 A command-line remote mail client with DKIM/DMARC/SPF support.
